snippet.description:
STARPOINT GEMINI 3 | COMING IN 2019 | It's gonna be epic!
Wishlist on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/977720/Starpoint_Gemini_3/

Put on your pilot’s helmet, grab your spaceship rudders and play the first official gameplay trailer of Starpoint Gemini 3, to get prepared for your new exciting adventure in the Gemini universe!

Engage in action-packed space battles, visit amazing worlds and encounter interesting characters to find the answers you seek. For the first time in the franchise, Starpoint Gemini 3 brings animated 3D, NPCs that you can interact with, and this time your path leads beyond Gemini as you get to explore two new planetary systems.

You are not alone on your journey. You have ADAH, a digital consciousness that runs your ship's computer and can download itself onto your drone, which you can then control in ADAH’s role to accomplish off-ship tasks you could never do alone. 

Buckle your seatbelts and prepare to immerse yourself in a world of space adventurer. Visit various venues, from pubs with shady clientele, to high-tech facilities and glitzy, noisy nightclubs, pick your targets and choose your allies. Your journey is about to begin. 

Key features:

- A huge immersive space spanning throughout three different planet systems of former imperial colonies;
- Large variety of characters with unique personalities, different questlines and factions;
- Adrenaline-packed dogfighting combat;
- Unique combat system that allows player mid-combat weapon switching;
- New out-of-ship drone control and exploration of space structures;
- Modular ship upgrading system;
- Complete set of RPG skills to boost player's capabilities over the course of the game;
- Detailed visitable interiors on different planets;
- Universe populated with unique areas, objects and characters that allow players to engage in many different activities while free-roaming between missions;
- Storyline is written by Darko Macan, the official writer for numerous Star Wars and Marvel comics.


--------------------

CONNECT WITH US!
Discord: https://discord.gg/StarpointGemini
Website: http://www.starpointgemini.com
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/StarpointGemini
Twitter: https://twitter.com/StarpointGemini
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/lgmgames/
LGM Games: https://lgmgames.net/

Don't forget to subscribe to our channel for future videos! :)


Starpoint Gemini 3 © 2019 Little Green Men Games. Developed by Little Green Men Games.
All brands, product names, and logos are trademarks or registered trademarks of their respective owners. All rights reserved. Made in Europe.

